flowchart TB

    Client["🖥️ ReMedi Web (PWA)<br/>React + Vite / Service Worker<br/>홈·복약관리·정보·LLM상담·설정 5탭"]
    Edge["NGINX<br/>Reverse Proxy / TLS"]
    API["⚙️ FastAPI Backend<br/>(Auth / Core / Chat / Safety / SQLAdmin)"]
    RAG["🔎 RAG Pipeline<br/>(Squad B 소유)"]
    Workers["🔁 Background Workers<br/>(Notification / Content / News / Report)"]
    Data["🗄️ Data Layer<br/>(RDS / Redis / ChromaDB / S3)"]
    External["🌍 External APIs<br/>(LLM / OCR / CLIP / TTS / Web Push)"]
    Ops["🛠️ CI/CD & Observability"]

    Client -->|HTTPS| Edge
    Edge --> API

    API --> RAG
    API --> Workers
    API --> Data
    API --> External

    RAG --> Data
    RAG --> External

    Workers --> Data
    Workers --> External

    Ops -.배포/모니터링.-> API
    Ops -.배포/모니터링.-> Workers
